descriptions.value: Hevði nakrar restir frá tá beiggji mín gjørdi lekkrar burgarar. So brukti restirnar til at gera eina skjóta pasta rætt
Had some leftovers from when my brother made some delishious burgers. So I used the leftovers to make a quick pasta dish

images.alt: A pasta dish with mince meat, croutons, bell peppers, and more.
